title: "Principle of Least Effort in AI Interpretation: A GEO Conceptual Model"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-04-17
url: "https://verri.pro/il-principio-del-minimo-sforzo-nell-interpretazione-delle-ia/"
repository-code: "https://github.com/alessandro-verri/principle-of-least-effort-ai"
abstract: >-
  An adaptation of Zipf's Principle of Least Effort to the field of Generative Engine 
  Optimization. It explains how AI systems minimize computational energy by 
  simplifying complex or inconsistent digital signals into generic representations.
